message: bump version, add authors to package.json
Some version updates; take react-native-branch from local copy instead of npm; add babel-preset-react-native devDependency
Corrected some issues in the podspec and package.json
Document release() method and update to version 1.1.0.
Added Release-2.0.0.md. Version number changed to 2.0.0-beta.1
Added eslint to .travis.yml and runAllTests. Also fixed some eslint issues.
pin some devDependencies to ~15.4.0 to eliminate deprecation warnings
Version bump to 2.0.0-beta.4 and URL corrections in package.json
Update to RN 0.43.1, React 16.0.0-alpha to fix unit test issues

message: Updated peer dependency to RN ^0.60.0. This breaks both Android and JS unit tests, to be restored later.
Removed package-lock.json. Fixes to devDeps in package.json
added plugin name and version on android
add plugin type and version on the iOS side
SDK-714 reuse iOS version update script to update android
SDK-693 update version to 4.3.0 since the native SDKs are jumping a few versions
Get rid of checkCachedEvents: true in testbed_simple
Update repo dependencies to RN 0.62.0, React 16.11.0.
One trivial test passing with jest 25.
Add bug report email address to package.json

Merge pull request #612 from runtrizapps/typescript-defs

feat: add TypeScript definition

Bump version for more community PRs

  - Null checks for listeners. Thanks ilyagru!
  - Depend on React-Core instead of React. Thanks radko93!
  - Use @ReactModule annotation. Thanks janicduplessis!

Update dependencies

  - Fix type definition of createBranchUniversalObject (Thanks v-fernandez!)
  - Update Android SDK to 5.1.0
  - Update iOS SDK to 1.41.0
  - Update other dependencies to latest non-breaking

Release 5.5.0

2022-07-20 Version 5.5.0
  - Branch QR code creation support added.
    ```js
    getBranchQRCode: (
    settings: BranchQRCodeSettings,
    branchUniversalObject: BranchUniversalObjectOptions,
    linkProperties: BranchLinkProperties,
    controlParams: BranchLinkControlParams,
  ) => Promise<string>;
  ```
  - Support for preinstall analytics.
    ```js
    setPreInstallCampaign = (campaign) => RNBranch.setPreinstallCampaign(campaign)
    setPreInstallPartner = (partner) => RNBranch.setPreinstallPartner(partner)
  ```
  - Update react-native to 0.63.0
  - Update Android SDK to 5.2.0
  - Update iOS SDK to 1.43.1

Release 5.6.0

2022-09-30 Version 5.6.0
  - Update Android SDK to 5.2.4
  - Update iOS SDK to 1.43.2
  - Fix BranchUniversalObject showShareSheet return type definition (thanks romanlitvin)
  - Change customData type definition to String String dictionary (thanks vincent-paing!)
  - Fixed clearPartnerParameters call (thanks danilobuerger!)
  - Add callback to setIdentity in new function `setIdentityAsync`
SDK-1697 update to iOS 1.45.1 and Android 5.2.6. This increases the iOS min version to iOS 11
